  <h2>Comprehensive Forensic Economics Services by Location</h2>
  <p>Skerritt Economics & Consulting provides expert forensic economics services throughout New England. Our economic damage analysis services are available in all major cities and regions, with consistent methodologies and court-tested approaches regardless of location.</p>
  <p>We understand the unique economic conditions, wage patterns, and employment markets in each state and city we serve, ensuring accurate and locally-relevant economic loss calculations.</p>
